{"tid":622433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★根據政府數字，露宿者數目較2013年增長4成 快餐店露宿者較13年增長5.7倍","createTime":"2018-04-09T06:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T08:02:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0d7d2330ff0bb142483a469dd17ad303fc1fc811","tid":622433,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"在立法會福利事務委員會上，社區組織協會的代表表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">根據政府數字，露宿者的最新數目較2013年增長4成，而協會去年底所做的統計發現，24小時快餐店露宿者約有384人，較13年增長達5.7倍</span>，質疑政府的服務及配套不足，難以幫助露宿者。<br />\n<br />\n街工的梁耀忠質疑，政府無針對解決露宿者問題，擔心會出現年輕化、女性化的情況。<br />\n<br />\n社署副署長彭潔玲表示，現時露宿者宿位使用率約為8成左右，如果宿位不足以應付，政府會再檢視規劃情況。她又說，露宿者問題涉及跨局跨部門，社署會繼續與其他部門處理跟進。<br />\n<br />\n彭潔玲又指，快餐店的露宿者增加，可能反映街上的露宿者減少，又指部分露宿者因天熱而到有冷氣的快餐店過夜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390167-20180409.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390167-20180409.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=zzcAzgRpBJJpPIykeAO1UwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=63c583e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1390167-20180409.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d6143be8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1390167-20180409.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e63bac8bf613bfd0fe0743da7344e9085834b32d","tid":622433,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c054a8f4e75e27ef7fef3f4798518f77061338","tid":622433,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"加左你未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d7a3e99623462659d0d84e292ec3ec9c38b250","tid":622433,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c054a8f4e75e27ef7fef3f4798518f77061338","tid":622433,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":